title: Biden calls for suspending normal trade relations with Russia and will ban imports of vodka and seafood - CNN
content:
1. Biden calls for suspending normal trade relations with Russia and will ban imports of vodka and seafood  CNN
  2. Biden calls for ending normal trade relations with Russia  NBC News
  3. Russia to lose 'most favored nation' trade status  Reuters
  4. US to ban Russian diamond and vodka imports  BBC.com
  5. Russian forces moving on Kyiv as fighting intensifies in Ukraine  Eyewitness News ABC7NY
  6. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: President Joe Biden on Friday called for suspending normal trade relations with Russia and said the US would ban imports of seafood, vodka and diamonds from the nation as part of an effort to ramp up economic pressure on Russia for invading Ukraine.
